Package: autonomics
Type: Package
Title: Generify and intuify omics data analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person("Aditya",   "Bhagwat",   email = "aditya.bhagwat@mpi-bn.mpg.de",    role = c("aut", "cre")), 
