Description: This package aims to make omics data analysis generic and intuitive, by implementing cross-platform
             analysis steps generically, and translating design information into relevant biological questions intuitively.
             It contains functions for data import, preprocessing, and analysis and currently offers support 
             for Microarray, RNAseq, LCMSMS Proteomics, Metabolon, and SOMAscan platforms.
